<main id=home>

  <h1 class='ui center aligned header'>TooLiP (Tools for Linguistic Productivity)</h1>

  <p>This website contains a collection of tools and utilities for working with linguistic data.</p>

  <section>

    <h2 class='ui header'>

      <svg class=transliterate-icon aria-labelledby=transliterate-header-title>
