        <use href=#svg-transliterate xlink:href=#svg-transliterate></use>
      </svg>

      <a href=/transliterator>Transliterator</a>

    </h2>

    <p>A web app for converting text from one writing system to another, a process known as <dfn>transliteration</dfn>. This app may also be used to remove unwanted characters or sequences of characters from a text, a process known as <dfn>sanitization</dfn> or <dfn>text cleaning</dfn>.</p>

  </section>

